{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"赵相浩Simon","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/qKwODFSJxd176zw0RXOcBcHPWKEk5vQgAbiby9cWBwluKlf8w3FfwXD3btuTZTWEXPz8fJOt7SZGdbvRhwoxHTjdqqEYlvuLQ/0","content":"<p>我是一个比较固执的人，我自己做的决定一定是经过了调研和分析的，因而我认为我的决定是正确的，是最好的，但事实上有时别人的建议的确非常有价值，聆听和吸纳别人的建议能够避免未来可能发生的很多问题。为了改变自己这一缺点我给自己取的英文名为Simon,Simon的含义是Listener，当别人给我提出意见时会说：“Simon, I think...”，所以Simon是一个很好的reminder来提醒我自己；其次我强迫自己在别人向我提出意见时等三秒再进行反馈，强迫自己对别人的意见进行思考。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7449,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491788917000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"郭舒简","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-09","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XRibESzncllLeNVVgOoXl3jmKXQT07IR1fYwPRIgiboTXU2tjiaAn3zpZ6cp8iaIvcTMxyrcwRR0P62w/0","content":"我比较年轻，和其他竞争者相比项目经验不多。但我的学习能力很强，对很多事物保持开放心态。我相信我可以通过参加实际项目提升能力，多和前辈交流得到他们的指点。当然具体问题都要具体分析，在实际项目中的冷静思考也是非常有必要的。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7410,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491698874000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Serena☀️","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyibmWFvpS4Srx56XicwoUSTK3t5icFPJ6cYsoKtNWJmsBHSmV1yAbz6XLoo3xVCnNx45KHnmzVJPojY/0","content":"面试猎头公司。<div>目前最大的缺点是，工作经验不足，与职场前辈面对面沟通时可能会有些信心不足。但是我的学习与适应能力很强，通过快速的学习行业知识以及对工作环境的适应，我相信逐渐便可以形成足够的信心。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5885,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491532018000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"放开那个小Joy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-23","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoPsccICKmhqibTHZ3c6PRPlXKQOMsQGCZVTGNkMa0625BIPiaGC4xAlvbRSOslvms4H38dWlfyorDL/0","content":"说一些与该岗位无关的“缺点”并说明目前在改进的简单情况。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5277,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490265049000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Evelyn","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-23","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZaLoY2RXU5FfnPYQicNKvU8piclQWvZStXH9QBFyxhlvc0JG22elM8ickAaGywcjhbN8GfGA1icDZvLMuglIsEHTrt/0","content":"最大的缺点是急于反馈或急于表达。\n在任务紧急的情况下，我会不自觉地倾向于及时给予对方反馈；但这样就造成对问题思考不够全面或者表达欠妥、缺乏条理性。\n针对这个缺点我也在积极弥补，比如参加了思维训练营、在日常中注意自己的思考或表达、向前辈寻求对接的技巧等等，目前有所好转。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5207,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490246712000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":true},"code":200}
